  "text": "We are now in a position to establish explicit necessary and sufficient conditions for a direct sum of uniform modules with local endomorphism rings to be a CS-module. For the last assertion of the theorem, see [CITATION_1] Corollary 3 .51 (cf. [8, 8.131 ). 0",
